{"tid":270013,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚見完家長 男朋友提出分手","createTime":"2017-06-04T05:09:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T11:09:50.000Z","uid":3066,"like":6,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dff6daaecb7a08eace31068dacc5a925f0b0ac7b","tid":270013,"uid":3066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:09:25.000Z","msg":"第一次見家長 佢阿媽一睇就係高氣質既人<br />\n食飯講起 知道我大學讀緊文科<br />\n男朋友讀商科 我地兩個唔夾<br />\n仲話睇死我個樣係要靠老公<br />\n生又生唔到蛋既人<br />\n<br />\n最終男朋友講左一句<br />\n阿媽得一個 女朋友可以再搵<br />\n佢阿媽覺得我地唔夾就唔夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d085ba77e345263d4bea08203025976cf3ed9054","tid":270013,"uid":53794,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:10:44.000Z","msg":"［巴打入］男士護膚及產品分享討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/178024/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/178024/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\nGay佬"},{"pid":"351780b14f6e2dcfb9a778765c8548f4971042a1","tid":270013,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:11:00.000Z","msg":"我知佢想為老母著重<br />\n但佢講完呢句有冇諗過對我幾hurt<br />\n吓 話散就散？<br />\n拍左拖未夠一年 當中無感情？"},{"pid":"6c37a4071ad9026de2b6df93e5a19734204c44d2","tid":270013,"uid":3066,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:11:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>［巴打入］男士護膚及產品分享討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/178024/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/178024/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\nGay佬</blockquote><br />\n之前幫男朋友護膚 呢家分左手<br />\n唔會再覆"},{"pid":"4cb02979cbf253c3c92bdb75e9f1ed3e310003ae","tid":270013,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:11:59.000Z","msg":"假膠"},{"pid":"5d792158acb20df0fd6efe2fb52abd1c99d4bae6","tid":270013,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:13:07.000Z","msg":"大學讀咩科關夾唔夾咩事, 佢老母無讀過咩叫和而不同咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma